      <div class="card-image">\n                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/300x200" alt="Card image">\n                </div>\n                <div class="card-content">\n                    <h3 class="card-title">Card Title 3</h3>\n                    <p class="card-description">This card has a much longer description to test how the grid handles different content heights and maintains visual consistency across all cards.</p>\n                    <button class="card-button">Learn More</button>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class="card">\n                <div class="card-image">\n                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/300x200" alt="Card image">\n                </div>\n                <div class="card-content">\n                    <h3 class="card-title">Card Title 4</h3>\n                    <p class="card-description">Another card with medium-length content to showcase the responsive behavior.</p>\n                    <button class="card-button">Learn More</button>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class="card">\n                <div class="card-image">\n                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/300x200" alt="Card image">\n                </div>\n                <div class="card-content">\n                    <h3 class="card-title">Card Title 5</h3>\n                    <p class="card-description">Final card example.</p>\n                    <button class="card-button">Learn More</button>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class="card">\n                <div class="card-image">\n                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/300x200" alt="Card image">\n                </div>\n                <div class="card-content">\n                    <h3 class="card-title">Card Title 6</h3>\n                    <p class="card-description">Last card to complete the grid demonstration.</p>\n                    <button class="card-button">Learn More</button>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n```\n\n### CSS Styles\n```css\n/* Reset and base styles */\n* {\n    margin: 0;\n    padding: 0;\n    box-sizing: border-box;\n}\n\nbody {\n    font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n    line-height: 1.6;\n    color: #333;\n    background-color: #f5f5f5;\n}\n\n.container {\n    max-width: 1200px;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n    padding: 2rem 1rem;\n}\n\nh1 {\n    text-align: center;\n    margin-bottom: 2rem;\n    color: #2c3e50;\n    font-size: 2.5rem;\n    font-weight: 300;\n}\n\n/* Card Grid System - Primary CSS Grid Implementation */\n.card-grid {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n    gap: 2rem;\n    margin-bottom: 2rem;\n}\n\n/* Flexbox fallback for older browsers */\n@supports not (display: grid) {\n    .card-grid {\n        display: flex;\n        flex-wrap: wrap;\n        gap: 2rem;\n        justify-content: center;\n    }\n    \n    .card {\n        flex: 1 1 300px;\n        max-width: 350px;\n    }\n}\n\n/* Individual Card Styles */\n.card {\n    background: white;\n    border-radius: 12px;\n    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n    overflow: hidden;\n    transition: all 0.3s ease;\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n    height: 100%; /* Ensures equal height cards */\n}\n\n.card:hover {\n    transform: translateY(-5px);\n    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);\n}\n\n/* Card Image */\n.card-image {\n    position: relative;\n    overflow: hidden;\n    height: 200px; /* Fixed height for consistent layout */\n}\n\n.card-image img {\n    width: 100%;\n    height: 100%;\n    object-fit: cover;\n    transition: transform 0.3s ease;\n}\n\n.card:hover .card-image img {\n    transform: scale(1.05);\n}\n\n/* Card Content */\n.card-content {\n    padding: 1.5rem;\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n    flex-grow: 1; /* Allows content to expand and fill available space */\n}\n\n.card-title {\n    font-size: 1.25rem;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;\n    color: #2c3e50;\n}\n\n.card-description {\n    color: #666;\n    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n    flex-grow: 1; /* Pushes button to bottom */\n    line-height: 1.5;\n}\n\n.card-button {\n    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);\n    color: white;\n    border: none;\n    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;\n    border-radius: 6px;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    font-weight: 500;\n    transition: all 0.3s ease;\n    align-self: flex-start;\n}\n\n.card-button:hover {\n    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #5a6fd8 0%, #6a4190 100%);\n    transform: translateY(-2px);\n}\n\n.card-button:active {\n    transform: translateY(0);\n}\n\n/* Responsive Breakpoints */\n\n/* Large screens (desktops) */\n@media (min-width: 1200px) {\n    .card-grid {\n        grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);\n    }\n}\n\n/* Medium screens (tablets) */\n@media (min-width: 768px) and (max-width: 1199px) {\n    .card-grid {\n        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);\n        gap: 1.5rem;\n    }\n    \n    .container {\n        padding: 1.5rem 1rem;\n    }\n}\n\n/* Small screens (mobile) */\n@media (max-width: 767px) {\n    .card-grid {\n        grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n        gap: 1rem;\n    }\n    \n    .container {\n        padding: 1rem 0.5rem;\n    }\n    \n    h1 {\n        font-size: 2rem;\n        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n    }\n    \n    .card-content {\n        padding: 1rem;\n    }\n    \n    .card-image {\n        height: 180px;\n    }\n}\n\n/* Extra small screens */\n@media (max-width: 480px) {\n    .card-grid {\n        gap: 0.75rem;\n    }\n    \n    .card-image {\n        height: 160px;\n    }\n    \n    h1 {\n        font-size: 1.75rem;\n    }\n}\n\n/* Accessibility improvements */\n@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {\n    .card,\n    .card-image img,\n    .card-button {\n        transition: none;\n    }\n    \n    .card:hover {\n        transform: none;\n    }\n    \n    .card:hover .card-image img {\n        transform: none;\n    }\n}\n\n/* Focus styles for keyboard navigation */\n.card:focus-within {\n    outline: 2px solid #667eea;\n    outline-offset: 2px;\n}\n\n.card-button:focus {\n    outline: 2px solid #667eea;\n    outline-offset: 2px;\n}\n```\n\n## How to Use\n\n1. **Basic Implementation**: Copy the HTML and CSS code into your project files.\n\n2. **Customization Options**:\n   - **Card Width**: Modify `minmax(300px, 1fr)` in the grid-template-columns to change minimum card width\n   - **Gap Size**: Adjust the `gap` property to increase/decrease spacing between cards\n   - **Colors**: Update the color variables and gradients to match your brand\n   - **Breakpoints**: Modify the media query breakpoints to suit your design needs\n\n3. **Adding More Cards**: Simply duplicate the `.card` HTML structure and add your content.\n\n4. **Dynamic Content**: The layout automatically adapts to varying content lengths while maintaining visual consistency.\n\n## Key Features\n\n- **Responsive Design**: Automatically adjusts from 4 columns on desktop to 1 column on mobile\n- **Equal Height Cards**: All cards in a row maintain the same height regardless of content length\n- **Smooth Animations**: Hover effects and transitions enhance user experience\n- **Accessibility**: Includes focus states and respects user motion preferences\n- **Browser Support**: Uses CSS Grid with flexbox fallback for older browsers\n- **Performance**: Efficient CSS with minimal reflows and repaints\n\nThe system is production-ready and can be easily integrated into any web project requiring a responsive card layout.	{}	2026-02-03 10:14:39.889002
